<h3>&#272;&#7883;nh d&#7841;ng th&#432;</h3>
<p>N&#7871;u b&#7841;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &quot;auto detect&quot;, th&#432; s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c coi l&agrave; HTML ngay sau khi m&#7897;t th&#7867; HTML (&lt;...&gt;) &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&igrave;m th&#7845;y.</p>
<p><b> S&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c coi l&agrave; an to&agrave;n n&#7871;u &#273;&#7875; l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n n&agrave;y l&agrave; &quot;Auto detect&quot;</b></p>
<p>N&#7871;u b&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7855;c r&#7857;ng &quot;auto detect&quot; s&#7869; l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c v&agrave; th&ocirc;ng &#273;i&#7879;p b&#7841;n &#273;ang s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;ang c&oacute; &#273;&#7883;nh d&#7841;ng HTML th&igrave; h&atilde;y ch&#7885;n &quot;HTML&quot;. &#272;&#432;&#7901;ng d&#7851;n tr&#7887; t&#7899;i c&aacute;c t&agrave;i nguy&ecirc;n b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i (v&iacute; d&#7909; h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh) ph&#7843;i s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng d&#7851;n tuy&#7879;t &#273;&#7889;i. T&#7913;c l&agrave; ph&#7843;i b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u v&#7899;i http://. Ngo&agrave;i ra b&#7841;n ph&#7843;i ch&#7855;c ch&#7855;n v&#7899;i c&aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh d&#7841;ng text c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh.</p>
<p>N&#7871;u b&#7841;n ch&#7881; mu&#7889;n g&#7917;i &#273;&#7883;nh d&#7841;ng text th&igrave; h&atilde;y ch&#7885;n &quot;Text&quot;</p>
<p>Th&ocirc;ng tin sau &#273;&acirc;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7875; chuy&#7875;n &#273;&#7893;i t&#7915; th&ocirc;ng &#273;i&#7879;p c&oacute; &#273;&#7883;nh d&#7841;ng HTML sang Text ho&#7863;c t&#7915; Text sang &#273;&#7883;nh d&#7841;ng HTML. Quy &#432;&#7899;c s&#7869; nh&#432; sau:<br>
  Th&ocirc;ng &#273;i&#7879;p l&agrave; HTML -&gt; text</p>
<ul>
  <li><b>Ch&#7919; &#273;&#7853;m</b> s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c bao b&#7903;i d&#7845;u <b>*</b>, ch&#7919; nghi&ecirc;ng v&#7899;i d&#7845;u<b> /</b></li>
  <li>&#272;o&#7841;n text c&oacute; li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thay th&#7871; b&#7903;i Text v&agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng d&#7851;n &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911; trong d&#7845;u ngo&#7863;c</li>
  <li>Kh&#7889;i v&#259;n b&#7843;n l&#7899;n s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ng&#7855;t d&ograve;ng t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng t&#7841;i c&#7897;t 70</li>
</ul>
<p>Th&ocirc;ng &#273;i&#7879;p l&agrave; Text -&gt; HTML</p>
<ul>
  <li>Hai ng&#7855;t d&ograve;ng s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thay b&#7903;i th&#7867; &lt;p&gt; (paragraph)</li>
  <li>Ng&#7855;t d&ograve;ng &#273;&#417;n s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thay b&#7903;i th&#7867; &lt;br /&gt; (line break)</li>
  <li>&#272;&#7883;a ch&#7881; email s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chuy&#7875;n th&agrave;nh d&#7841;ng &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; th&#7875; b&#7845;m chu&#7897;t.</li>
  <li>&#272;&#7883;a ch&#7881; trang web s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chuy&#7875;n th&agrave;nh d&#7841;ng &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; th&#7875; b&#7845;m chu&#7897;t. &#272;&#7883;a ch&#7881; web c&oacute; th&#7875; l&agrave;:
    <ul>
      <li> http://some.website.url/some/path/somefile.html</li>
      <li> www.websiteurl.com </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>
<p>Li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#7841;o ra s&#7869; c&oacute; ki&#7875;u &quot;url&quot; v&agrave; th&ocirc;ng s&#7889; target &quot;_blank&quot;.</p>
<p><b>Ch&uacute; &yacute;</b>: ch&#7881; &#273;&#7883;nh th&ocirc;ng &#273;i&#7879;p l&agrave; Text nh&#432;ng l&#7841;i d&aacute;n m&#7897;t &#273;o&#7841;n Text c&oacute; &#273;&#7883;nh d&#7841;ng HTML s&#7869; g&#7917;i c&aacute;c m&atilde; HTML t&#7899;i ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng mu&#7889;n nh&#7853;n th&ocirc;ng &#273;i&#7879;p c&oacute; &#273;&#7883;nh d&#7841;ng Text. Nh&#432; v&#7853;y s&#7869; r&#7845;t kh&oacute; &#273;&#7885;c.</p>
